WEBVTT

00:10:28.942 --> 00:10:30.661
D'acord, farem el següent:

00:10:31.005 --> 00:10:32.404
comptaré fins a tres

00:10:32.748 --> 00:10:33.899
i quan acabi,

00:10:33.923 --> 00:10:35.940
us demano que tots

00:10:36.114 --> 00:10:38.979
deixeu anar el vostre crit més fan.

00:10:39.003 --> 00:10:40.161
(Riures)

00:10:40.185 --> 00:10:41.101
D'acord?

00:10:41.215 --> 00:10:43.235
Us ho demano per una raó:

00:10:43.609 --> 00:10:49.204
si les cinc mil persones
que som aquí ho fem,

00:10:49.228 --> 00:10:53.093
tenim la oportunitat de sentir el so

00:10:53.117 --> 00:10:55.946
i decidir que no és una cosa de bojos,

00:10:56.577 --> 00:10:58.044
és un so d'esperança.

00:10:58.577 --> 00:10:59.911
Ho fem?